  <brief_title>Solid Tumor Cancer Surgery With or Without Intraoperative Imaging: A Registry</brief_title>
  <official_title>Solid Tumor Cancer Surgery With or Without Intraoperative Imaging: A Registry Optional Sub-Study I: ICG Optional Sub-Study II: OTL38</official_title>
  <sponsors>
