  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study objective is to collect prospective data on cancer patients who undergo surgery and
      intraoperative imaging. The registry will include (but not limited to) cancer type, stage,
      intraoperative challenges to the surgeon, usage and results of intraoperative imaging, and
      recurrence surveillance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
